### Configure Playwright global baseURL in playwright.config.ts

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-use-options-js.md

This code sets a global `baseURL` in the Playwright configuration file, `playwright.config.ts`. The `baseURL` is placed within the `use` property of `defineConfig`, making it available to all tests unless overridden.

```js
import { defineConfig } from '@playwright/test';

export default defineConfig({
  use: {
    baseURL: 'https://playwright.dev'
  }
});
```

